-- Chelsea Signs Belgian Midfielder Eden Hazard, Soccer Club Says
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2012-06-04T16:15:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-04/chelsea-signs-belgian-midfielder-eden-hazard-soccer-club-says.html
Chelsea signed Belgian midfielder
Eden Hazard from Lille as the London club re-tools after winning
the Champions League last season.  The 21-year-old Hazard will join in July after the end of
the European Championship, Chelsea said today on its website. He
scored 21 times in 48 games for Lille last season.  Chelsea also signed German national team member Marko Marin
for next season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  